<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    {{> ./_includes/head}}
    <style>
      .demo-hero {
        background: url('/img/background.png');
        background-size: cover;
        min-height: 400px;
        padding: 0;
        margin: 0;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
        flex-direction: column;
        color: white;
      }
      .below-menu {
        padding-top: 144px;
      }
      .hero-info {
        max-width: 502px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        text-align: center;
      }
      .action-button {
        background: transparent;
        width: 192px;
        height: 57px;
        border-radius: 4px;
        border: 2px solid #ffffff;
        color: #ffffff;
        font-family: "Open Sans";
        font-size: 16px;
        line-height: 24px;
        letter-spacing: -0.2px;
        margin: 8px;
        padding-top: 0px;
      }
      .action-button:hover {
        cursor: pointer;
        padding-bottom: 5px;
        transition: all .1s ease;
      }
      .white-b {
        background: white;
        color: #e45b6b;
      }
      .action-buttons {
        display: flex;
        margin-top: 24px;
        flex-direction: row;
        justify-content: center;
        margin-bottom: 48px;
      }
      .my-title {
        font-family: "Open Sans";
        font-size: 32px;
        font-weight: 700;
        /* Text style for "MLH Local" */
        letter-spacing: -0.2px;
        margin-top: 32px;
        margin-bottom: 8px;
      }
      .hero-logo {
        margin-top: 50px;
      }
      .content-wrapper {
        margin-top: 64px;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: row;
        margin-bottom: 64px;
      }
      .left-content {
        padding-right: 20px;
        width: 50%;
      }
      .right-content {
        padding-left: 20px;        
        width: 50%;        
      }
      .video {
        width: 500px;
      }
      .video-info {
        color: #959595;
        font-family: "Open Sans";
        font-size: 16px;
        line-height: 24px;
        /* Text style for "Watch MLH'" */
        letter-spacing: -0.2px;
      }
    </style>
  </head>

  <body {{#if htmlWebpackPlugin.options.site.title}} class="{{ htmlWebpackPlugin.options.site.custom_class }}" {{/if}}>

    {{> ./_includes/main_nav}}

    <div class="demo-hero below-menu">
      <img class="hero-logo" src="/img/logos/localhost-logo.png">
      <h1 class="my-title">MLH Local Hack day</h1>
      <div class="content">
        <p class="hero-info">While these events don't have all the same resources a Member</p>
        <p class="hero-info">Event gets, they'll still be a great experience for hackers!</p>
        <div class="action-buttons">
          <button class="action-button white-b">Submit Project</button>
          <button class="action-button">Find Event</button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <div class="content-wrapper">
        <div class="left-content">
          <div class="content-item">
            <h4>MLH Local Hack Day</h4>
            <p>
              Here are some other links that may be useful throughout the day. Below you will find everything from how to submit your project to how to stay in touch with other hackers and more!
            </p>
            <p>
              <a>Connect with the Community on Slack</a> - Join our Slack channel to connect with other hackers and ask for mentorship.
            </p>
            <p>
              <a>Submit your project on Devpost</a> - Post your project on our official DevPost page to share what you made this weekend with the world!
            </p>
            <p>
              <a>Code of Conduct</a> - At MLH we believe that hackathons should be safe and welcoming spaces. This event, like all MLH events, is under the official MLH Code of Conduct, which you can read here.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="right-content">
          <img class="video" src="img/video.png">
          <p class="video-info">
            Watch MLH's co-founder, Jon Gottfried, welcome everyone to Local Hack Day. Jon covers what to expect throughout the day and the awesome resources that are available through MLH and our sponsors.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    {{> ./_includes/footer}}
  </body>
</html>